erpt_area": {"text": "据界面新闻消息，6 月 27 日，特斯拉中国区最近两天启动了召回此前被裁掉员工的流程，预计召回规模超过 100 人，由于这项工作刚开始启动，召回的人数可能出现变化。目前，计划召回的员工原本归属于充电、销售、售后和交付部门，如果同意被召回，返岗员工需要退还「N+3」裁员赔偿部分的「3」，且司龄重新计算。 当地时间 4 月 15 日，特斯拉首席执行官埃隆·马斯克在一封致员工的内部电子邮件中透露该公司将裁减超过 10% 的全球员工，以削减成本并提高生产率。 特斯拉中国区也受到影响，但裁员比例超过 10%，充电、销售和市场团队的裁员比例甚至有达到 40%-50%。对于被裁员工，特斯拉的赔偿标准是「N+3」，并在谈好裁员赔偿条件的当天就办理手续离开办公室。5 月底，特斯拉中国陆续发放裁员赔偿。闪电快讯 ｜ 特斯拉中国召回被裁员工：赔偿金退「3」，涉及充电、销售、售后和交付"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-14086d2709d8d40f13c9c8b3674ed5e6_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660154060"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIvoD+gdrO+p9BEAMaCTEwODk3ODgyOSD1t/izBjAAOKECQBFyCTY2MDE1NDA2MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1719613121.861305", "card_id": "Q_647060573", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 76}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "被占有欲很强的病娇喜欢上是一种什么体验？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/647060573"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIvoD+gdrO+p9BEAMaCTEwNjA2ODU2MSDumJevBjAAOP8BQBJyCTY0NzA2MDU3M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1719613121.861522", "card_id": "Q_660065800", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 107}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "文笔挑战：「我在等，等…」怎么接下一句?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-9f757503354485fffdccf91472b1609f_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"