者 刘晓琰）日本决定将大陆架扩大 12 万平方公里，外交部回应"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f1b6021ecddbed9e445c61287a60fb3b_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660078666"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIvoD+gdrO+p9BEAMaCTEwODk2MjA0NyDZvfSzBjAAOK4FQBpyCTY2MDA3ODY2NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1719613121.865465", "card_id": "Q_660013987", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 104}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价综艺《歌手 2024》第八期歌手们的表现？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "《The Best》香缇莫 《一颗星的夜》那英 《无言感激》孙楠 《听见下雨的声音》汪苏泷 《来自天堂的魔鬼》凡希亚 《Close To You》黃宣 《二十二》袁娅维 《兰花花儿》谭维维 《All By Myself》露西娅"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-2877bce20a32093865ec334b4d87580d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "44 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660013987"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IvoD+gdrO+p9BEAMaCTEwODk0NzYyMCCFv/CzBjAAOHlAG3IJNjYwMDEzOTg3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1719613121.866047", "card_id": "Q_659949090", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 63}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "婚姻幸福的女人，是因为有一个好老公吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "有人说: 对女人而言，婚姻有时宛如一场赌局。那些运气不错的女性，押对了一个好老公，日子过得很美好。而运气欠佳的，则可能每天都在家庭纷扰中过得十分压抑。你怎么看？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-a9440f61b1ea479c6199ee29b18c5f99_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "36 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/659949090"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IvoD+gdrO+p9BEAMaCTEwODkzMz